hopobject.body: Do you know what extension he's on? endowmax oil reviews While the added inches in his vertical leap are a nice thing for breakaway dunks, him feeling confident in finishing through contact and not worrying if his body will be able to take the pounding on those plays is probably more important. Rose needs to feel like he can absorb contact and still convert shots in the paint. It's how he ended up with 10 free throw attempts in 22 minutes Wednesday night and that's how he'll truly get back to his dominant self.
